99
00:06:09,052 --> 00:06:10,653
A whole week?

100
00:06:10,654 --> 00:06:12,522
Because the zipper
was stuck.

101
00:06:12,523 --> 00:06:14,590
He didn't mean to do it.

102
00:06:14,591 --> 00:06:16,091
He bumped
around the house

103
00:06:16,092 --> 00:06:18,761
