for a whole week.

104
00:06:18,762 --> 00:06:20,696
I got to run.

105
00:06:20,697 --> 00:06:22,965
What do you mean,
you got to run?

106
00:06:22,966 --> 00:06:24,634
Daddy,
it's my birthday.

107
00:06:24,635 --> 00:06:26,902
