shaving cream?

109
00:06:29,172 --> 00:06:30,673
You completely
forgot, bucko.
Admit it.

110
00:06:30,674 --> 00:06:32,207
Oh, yeah?

111
00:06:32,208 --> 00:06:33,877
Yeah.

112
00:06:39,215 --> 00:06:40,816
Thursday,

113
00:06:40,817 --> 00:06:45,187
