117
00:06:53,530 --> 00:06:54,530
Really?

118
00:06:54,531 --> 00:06:55,565
Yes.

119
00:06:55,566 --> 00:06:56,533
Really?

120
00:06:56,534 --> 00:06:57,800
Yes.

121
00:06:57,801 --> 00:06:59,635
Daddy, can I
drive it today?

122
00:06:59,636 --> 00:07:00,970
I'll be
incredibly careful.

123
00:07:00,971 --> 00:07:02,572
