202
00:10:52,035 --> 00:10:54,069
How are you, sir?

203
00:10:54,070 --> 00:10:57,373
Oh, yes. I'm eating
solid food again.

204
00:10:59,042 --> 00:11:00,509
Oh, well,

205
00:11:00,510 --> 00:11:02,077
wonderful!

206
00:11:02,078 --> 00:11:04,013
We'll see you
at the bankers' at 10:00.

207
00:11:04,014 --> 00:11:05,014
G'day, sir.

208
00:11:05,015 --> 00:11:06,249
G'day, sir.

