I'm trying to quit.

229
00:12:45,015 --> 00:12:47,582
Haah!

230
00:12:47,583 --> 00:12:49,119
Uhh!

231
00:12:56,392 --> 00:12:58,393
Ow!

232
00:12:58,394 --> 00:13:01,030
Do you accept
the lord Satan

233
00:13:01,031 --> 00:13:02,531
